data.description: 3 bedroom / 2 bathroom site built home nestled on 0.7 acres just minutes from the LMU Vet Campus. Home has a covered front porch and a spacious new covered back deck that is completely screened-in so you can enjoy the beautiful mountain views. Fenced back yard. High Speed Internet through PVEC Fiber. Large walk-in closets throughout. Storage Shed conveys with property.  Seller will purchase a Home Warranty Plan for the buyer.
